project_descr: Fourth phase of UNDP's multi-donor programme for conflict-affected communities in Mindanao in support of the 1996 GPH-MNLF Final Peace Agreement

outputs.output_descr: The Action for Conflict Transformation (ACT) for Peace Programme aims to strengthen peace-building efforts and sustain the gains for peace and development in Southern Philippines

Strengthens response to prevent displacement, promotion of rights of Internally Displaced Persons (IDP), and effective delivery of assistance to vulnerable communities, comprising of IDPs and host communities
